Remember to replace `<YOUR_GCP_PROJECT_ID>` and `<YOUR_CONTAINER_IMAGE>` with your actual Google Cloud Platform project ID and container image URL. This config assumes you've already set up a Kafka service to receive logs and send them to a Cloud Run service, which can then push them to Pub/Sub. You may need to adjust the configurations to fit your specific use case, including IAM permissions, service account details, and the cloud run image used for logging.

